'''fractal'''
#{{mathematics}} a [[geometric]] [[figure]] that appears [[irregular]] at all [[scale]]s of [[length]]
#{{mathematics}} a geometric figure, built up from a simple shape, by [[generating]] the same or similar changes on [[successively]] [[smaller]] scales; it shows [[self-similarity]] on all scales

